<button class="pg-search-trigger">
  <span>Search</span>
</button>
<button class="pg-menu-trigger">
  <span>Menu</span>
</button>
<div class="pg-accordion" data-pg-accordion>
  {% for i in 1..3 %}
    <div class="pg-accordion__slide" data-pg-accordion-slide>
      <h1>Accordion Item {{ i }} Title</h1>
      <div class="pg-accordion__content" data-pg-accordion-content>
        <p>Accordion Item {{ i }} content</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="hilm-scroller" data-hilm-scroller>
    <div class="hilm-scroller__head" data-hilm-scroller-head>
      <h2>Featured Insights</h2>
      <h6 class="hilm-type-emphasis">
        As featured in Hiscox Global Insight</h6>
    </div>
    <div class="row hilm-scroller__row">
      <div class="col-md-6 hilm-scroller__main" data-hilm-scroller-main>
        <div class="hilm-story" style="background-image: url('/themes/custom/hiscox_londonmarket/img/placeholder/hero.jpg');">
          <div class="hilm-story__content">
            <h6 class="hilm-type-label">Space Tourism</h6>
            <h2>Iran: Open for business?</h2>
            <a class="hilm-button" href="/">Read the article</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 hilm-scroller__inset">
        <div class="row hilm-scroller__inset-row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="/themes/custom/hiscox_londonmarket/img/placeholder/hero.jpg"/>
            <h3>Working the niches</h3>
            <p>From insuring Danish dog owners to wind turbine operators, our Alternative Distribution team is on the hunt for new risks.</p>
            <div class="hilm-block-wrapper">
              <a class="hilm-cta" href="/">Read more</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="/themes/custom/hiscox_londonmarket/img/placeholder/tall.jpg"/>
            <h3>Outside the Box: Neil Bolton</h3>
            <p>Hiscox London Markets Head of Casualty on living the good life in the countryside, coping with vanishing hens and
                                                  suicidal sheep.</p>
            <div class="hilm-block-wrapper">
              <a class="hilm-cta" href="/">Read more</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="/themes/custom/hiscox_londonmarket/img/placeholder/hero.jpg"/>
            <h3>Open all hours: Hiscox drive terrorism trading online</h3>
            <p>Jade Gradwell explains why Hiscox's online terrorism initiative has improved accessibility and creates more time to meet
                                                  brokers.</p>
            <div class="hilm-block-wrapper">
              <a class="hilm-cta" href="/">Read more</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="/themes/custom/hiscox_londonmarket/img/placeholder/hero.jpg"/>
            <h3>The perils of being a wine-collecting addict</h3>
            <p>Collecting can be very addictive, says Bobby Read. Passionate wine collectors need to beware of where they get their
                                                  fixes.</p>
            <div class="hilm-block-wrapper">
              <a class="hilm-cta" href="/">Read more</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
